title: Avengers Arena (01 - 18) (complete) (- Nem -)
description:
A Marvel NOW! title.

Trapped on an isolated island, 16 superhuman young adults (including cult faves like members of The Runaways, The Avengers Academy and Darkhawk) are given a chilling ultimatum by their demented captor: Fight or die...only one will walk out alive!

Written by Dennis Hopeless

Art by Kevin Walker (#1-3, #5 onwards), Alessandro Vitti (#4)
